node.text:
She lives in daydreams with me, she's the first one that I see, and I don't know why
I don't know who she is
Sunflowers sometimes keep it sweet in your memory; your flowers just died, plant new seeds in the melody 🌻

Tastes like strawberries on a summer evenin'
And it sounds just like a song 💌

Does it ever drive you crazy
Just how fast the night changes 🖤
Words are flowing out like endless rain into a paper cup.
We don't know where we're going, but we know where we belong 🌸💐
One sunny day the world was waiting for a lover 💌

Los médanos serán témpanos
en el vértigo de la eternidad
y los pájaros serán arboles
en lo idéntico de la soledad.

Now the darkness only stays at nighttime
In the morning it will fade away 🌾
Little darling, it's been a long cold lonely winter 🌸🌱

El misterio es contradicción
con todo aquello que conoces.
Listen to the pretty sound of music as she flies.x
All day long I'm sitting singing songs for everyone.x

La mediocridad para algunos es normal
La locura es poder ver más allá.
